# Financial Management Tool

Welcome to the Financial Management Tool repository! This tool is designed to help you collect, aggregate, and organize your financial data into a digestible format to better manage your personal finances. Whether you're tracking expenses, monitoring income, or setting budgets, this tool provides an efficient way to gain insights into your financial health.

## Features

- **Data Collection**: Easily input your financial transactions, income sources, and expenses.
- **Aggregation**: Automatically categorize transactions and generate summaries.
- **Budgeting**: Set and manage budgets for different categories and track your progress.
- **Visualization**: Visualize your financial data through charts and graphs.
- **Reports**: Generate reports to analyze your financial habits over time.
- **Goal Setting**: Set financial goals and track your progress toward achieving them.
